OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAssam shorts: India        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fteenager forced to cover   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Flegs with curtain at exam  
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A 19-year-old Indian student who turned
OL,6, up in shorts to take an exam was forced
OL,7, to wrap a curtain around her legs after
OL,8, the teacher objected to her clothes.   
OL,10,FJublee Tamuli had travelled 70km (43   
OL,11,Fmiles) from her home for the exam in   
OL,12,FAssam's Tezpur town with her father,   
OL,13,Freports in the local press said.       
OL,15,FHer father rushed to a market to buy a 
OL,16,Fpair of trousers, but she said she took
OL,17,Fthe curtain since the test was timed.  
OL,19,FShe later described it as the "most    
OL,20,Fhumiliating experience of my life".    
